"{\"uid\": \"perthnow.com.au-news-business-retail-click-frenzy-travel-sale-olympics-making-you-want-to-go-to-paris-huge-deals-on-travel-kick-off-tonight-c-15621451\", \"text\": \"Get the FREE App  Get the FREE App  Planning to get away from your winter blues?  Well, here's your sign and a chance to do it on the cheap!  Click Frenzy Travel is launching Wednesday at 5pm WST and offering can not-miss deals, including discounted flights to Paris.  The sale - which will run until 10pm on August 10 - features the best travel providers and their deals across all the major travel categories including flights, accommodation, destination packages, cruises, experiences, tours, and luggage and accessories.  Notable brands offering top travel deals include Jetstar, Celebrity Cruises, RedBalloon, G Adventures, Expedia, Malaysia Airlines, Qatar Airways, Wendy Wu Tours, Oaks Hotels, Greyhound Australia and Scoopon.  Click Frenzy Head of Marketing Daniel Thompson said Australians are cutting costs across the board but surprisingly \\\"travel is not one of them\\\".  \\\"Aussies are prioritising taking trips - whether local or international - because they are craving that element of fun and escapism in their lives,\\\" he said.  \\\"We are thrilled to be bringing back some amazing travel deals to Australians with another sale this year. We have you covered, from incredible international flight deals to discounts at top-notch local hotels.\\\"  TOP-FLIGHT DEALS:  \\u25cfQatar Airways: 12 per cent off flights to Paris and other European destinations  \\u25cfJetstar: Fly to Japan and Return for FREE  TOP-CRUISE DEALS:  \\u25cfNorwegian Cruise Lines: Save up to $2,500 off Cruises to Europe, Hawaii, Asia and more!  \\u25cfCelebrity Cruises: Save up to 75 per cent Off Second Guest, and additional savings of up to $300 per room  \\u25cf Quark Expeditions 40 per cent off select Arctic and Antarctic voyages to Canadian Arctic to Greenland to Svalbard  TOP EXPERIENCES & PACKAGE DEALS:  \\u25cf